{"tid":1463020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再話民心唔緊要啊","createTime":"2019-08-13T11:53:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T12:08:14.000Z","uid":149563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a17c70ef44e708150920e8bbe36529d4e7259663","tid":1463020,"uid":149563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:53:57.000Z","msg":"從來革命嘅成功都係要有大部份市民嘅支持<br />\n你得民心就會贏㗎啦<br />\n你望下點解依家啲狗俾人當過街老鼠？<br />\n就係因為佢哋失民心啊<br />\n唔好再話咩而家呢一刻仲理咩民意<br />\n民意好緊要啊！<br />\n大家唔好因為一個錯嘅決定而令到整場運動失敗<br />\n咁樣會好對唔住被捕同埋已經唔喺度嘅手足<br />\n唔該你地吖<br />\n仲有唔好太心急 革命唔係一兩日就可以成功<br />\n大家俾啲耐性好唔好？<br />\n加油啊大家"},{"pid":"19e39d5bf4b0c6870fe6cf09d1605c95598dd250","tid":1463020,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:56:46.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8e94618bea5e4cf9320d3e6f492f38149fafa7f","tid":1463020,"uid":197563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:05:05.000Z","msg":"無人記得共產黨點得天下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8abccd5e7c551703cbaa815714e5a9428bbd43fe","tid":1463020,"uid":21552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:05:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a594d4626a10553337c086c3d40d67281ddb4070","tid":1463020,"uid":21552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8e94618bea5e4cf9320d3e6f492f38149fafa7f","tid":1463020,"uid":197563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:05:05.000Z","msg":"無人記得共產黨點得天下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:06:36.000Z","msg":"係文宣王<br />\n得天下時唔係咁強硬"},{"pid":"8223f4befaf52c23ba1a3d13aa694c49c8586093","tid":1463020,"uid":305822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:08:14.000Z","msg":"點解冇人